`Trivialization.smoothAt (e : Trivialization F (π F E)) [MemTrivializationAtlas e] {x₀ : TotalSpace F E} (hx₀ : x₀.proj ∈ e.baseSet) : ContMDiffAt (IB.prod 𝓘(𝕜, F)) (IB.prod 𝓘(𝕜, F)) ∞ e x₀`

